snippet.title: Zodiac XX  Leo - Official Reveal Trailer | Future of Play 2024
snippet.description: “ZODIAC XX: LEO” is an explosive underwater arcade piloting sci-fi thriller full of revolutionary energy and high-flying action. You command the infamous Zodiac Squadron, piloting ultra-manueverable submarine jet crafts - your wingman's lives are persistent through your playthrough, and their lives are in your hands. Perform dazzling aerials above the surface, manage your hull integrity in the the treacherous depths, and sustain eye-watering G-forces at submach speeds.
